com.camerontec.catalys.core.fixvalidation

Class MessageRuleSetValidator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.core.fixvalidation.AbstractValidatorWithAttributes
      • com.camerontec.catalys.core.fixvalidation.AbstractValidatorContainerWithAttributes
        • com.camerontec.catalys.core.fixvalidation.MessageRuleSetValidator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IObjectContainer, IValidator, IValidatorContainerWithAttributes, IValidatorWithAttributes, IHasAttributes

    public class MessageRuleSetValidator
extends AbstractValidatorContainerWithAttributes
    A validator container that contains instances of MessageValidator. It selects a child to call by examining the message's type and calling the child that handles that type (see MessageValidator.getMsgType()).

    If the mustMatch attribute is true, then it will throw a MessageException if there is no corresponding validator for the message type.
